“intend,” “may,” “outlook,” “plan,” “positioned,” “possible,” “potential,” “project,” “should,” “target,”
“will,” “would,” and similar expressions or variations thereof, or the negative thereof, but these terms
are not the exclusive means of identifying such statements. Forward-looking statements are based on
management’s expectations and assumptions as of the date of this report and are not guarantees of
future performance. You are cautioned not to place undue reliance on our forward-looking statements.
