revenue, margins, expenses, earnings, tax provisions, cash ﬂows, pension obligations, share repurchases
or other statements regarding economic conditions or our business outlook; statements regarding
capital expenditures and plans, projects, strategies and objectives for our future operations, including
our ability to win new projects and execute the projects in our backlog; and statements regarding our
expectations with respect to pending legal claims or disputes. While forward-looking statements are
